{"tid":128512,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最乞人憎巴士鄰坐","createTime":"2017-02-21T01:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T09:25:48.000Z","uid":61586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b13f6edecf1b391ec061c941c7bf0c6e01012fff","tid":128512,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"佢老味啲三手煙啊叔,臭到仆街,又成日咳到BOOMBOOM聲唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲師奶,日日係巴士度大大聲講自己野,我唔想知啊屌你老味,我想訓陣咋。<br />\n<br />\n仲有果啲死肥婆,你老味肥唔係原罪,你咁肥仲迫埋黎,仲用手爭頂撚住我條腰都算,你訓撚到好似啲卡通人物咁伸哂脷,左右FING頭係乜撚野事?洗唔洗CALL白車?<br />\n最撚慘係大大件唔俾人落車果度仆街。同你講唔該借借又嘖鳩我。<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲鼻鼾阿叔,係人都知扯鼻鼾好易有睡眠窒息,你有好節奏咁扯我都算,忍你,扯扯下突然好似窒息咁,嚇死我。"},{"pid":"0bce8482a0af5fd7013d58a9b2d8ad94e67a86d5","tid":128512,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"樓主果然鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌柒佢麻 上黎開Post托咩"},{"pid":"0d8ef64faeb243dca1fb2a3eea204b7d1cd48206","tid":128512,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:19:38.000Z","msg":"煙味5,60後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a5dfc0c8fe3d86cbd1299e8a6ee5f1b63df3dc","tid":128512,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主果然鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌柒佢麻 上黎開Post托咩</blockquote><br />\n成車人係度訓緊,屌柒佢咪盞俾人屌返轉頭<br />\n不過肥婆我係鬧過,一頭撞落我膊頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個頭又油,件衫都唔想要<br />\n我就鬧鳩佢「返屋企訓啦,架巴士係你張床咩仆街」之類<br />\n雖然鬧完我轉左位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc62831bb33558efacd42f3129a5d3ff6420cc7","tid":128512,"uid":20842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"搞到成個大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a0f10ca460d5de6507be08ab4f32d90bdebd6c","tid":128512,"uid":20842,"like":0,"di